title: Policy5470(10)
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

RSD 8 values and promotes community partnerships to enhance the overall health and wellness opportunities provided for students, families and staff. To that end, the Health and Wellness Committee shall continue to grow community participation to expand both the committee's membership as well as the programs and services afforded all students, families and staff in RSD 8.
